        [
          "Abigail- You feel an odd connection to the Pack priest and do not fear that she knows your secrets"
        ],
        [
          "Alabastor- The Pack leader keeps your secrets and relies on your strength to keep the others in line"
        ],
        [
          "Mr. Sticks- He doesn't suspect, you destroyed his old master in NY.  You hope to replace him as Abbot"
        ],
        [
          "Rachel- Albastor's thin blood progeny. She considers herself a warrior but you suspect that her bravado is an act to impress Alabastor and Abigail"
